y [[Adeel Hashmi]] and directed by [[Jawad Bashir (director)|Jawad Bashir]]. It was aired on [[Pakistan Television Corporation]] (PTV One, now [[PTV Home]]).<ref>{{cite web|title=Information of the sitcom|url=http://www.ptvdramas.com/comedy-serials/teen-bata-teen/|publisher=ptvdramas.com|accessdate=9 February 2013}}</ref>\n\n==Overview==\nTeen Bata Teen was aired in 1995 on [[PTV Home]] and it starred [[Adeel Hashmi]], [[Faisal Qureshi (comedian)|Faisal Qureshi]], Ali Tahir, Mira Hashmi, Wajiha Tahir and Fatima. The sitcom became very popular and was also named as the first television sitcom aired in [[Pakistan]].<ref>{{cite web|title=What He Does|url=http://www.adeelhashmi.pk/what-does-he-do/|website=AdeelHashmi.pk|accessdate=2 January 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author1=Zoya Anwer|title=6 Pakistani comedy shows that need to make a comeback|url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1184967|website=[[Dawn (newspaper)|DAWN]]|accessdate=2 January 2016|date=31 May 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author1=Rafay Mahmood|title=Pakistani TV today: Can we go beyond ratings?|url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/308390/pakistani-tv-today-can-we-go-beyond-ratings/|website=[[The Express Tribune]]|accessdate=2 January 2016|date=18 December 2011}}</ref>\n\nCast\n* [[Adeel Hashmi]] as Luci\n* [[Faisal Qureshi (director)|Faisal Qureshi]] as Shafu\n* Shahid Mehmood as Timmy\n* Ali Tahir as Johnny\n* Mira Hashmi as Mehreen\n* Wajiha Tahir as Beenish\n* Fatima as Zara\n* [[Jawad Bashir]]\n* [[Salman Shahid]]\n* Mudasir Aftab saghri\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{imdb title|5301618}}\n\n{{PTV Programs}}\n[[Category:Pakistani drama television series]]\n[[Category:Pakistani comedy television series]]\n[[Category:Urdu-language television programs]]\n[[Category:Pakistan Television Corporation shows]]\n[[Category:Pakistani television sitcoms]]\n\n{{Pakistan-tv-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Use Pakistani English|date=June 2015}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=June 2015}}\n{{Infobox television\n| sho